    <p>Things I learned over the night</p>
    <p class="fragment">
      Actually, I've learned it before, but forgotten, now it's documented'
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <p>
      Our <code>DEL</code>, <code>PATCH</code> &amp; <code>POST</code> requests return
      nothing
    </p>
    <p>If we add a <code>header</code> with</p>
    <p><code>Prefer: return=representation</code></p>
    <p>It does</p>
    <p class="fragment">As an array</p>
  </section>
  <section>
    <p>Live-Server on mobile?</p>
    <ol>
      <li>Start your live server</li>
      <li>Remember the http://127.0.0.1<code>:port</code></li>
      <li>
        Go to WiFi settings and find your local IP address<br />
        <a
          href="https://medium.com/@pavankapoor31/how-to-use-vs-code-live-server-local-host-on-mobile-phone-8b38a62117d2"
          >Here's how on Windows</a
        >
